import React, {Component} from 'react'
import { Button, Container, Row, Col, Form } from 'react-bootstrap';

 class Newissue extends Component {

    constructor(props) {
        super(props)
    
        this.state = {
             title:""
        }
    }

    handleChange=(event) =>{
        var name=event.target.name;
        console.log(name);
        this.setState({title: event.target.value});
      }
    

 render() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Form>
                <hr />
                <Form.Group as={Row} >
                    <Form.Label column sm="2">
                        Title
                    </Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="10">
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Title" name="title" value={this.state.title} onChange={this.handleChange}/>
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Row} >
                    <Form.Label column sm="2">Description</Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="10">
                        <Form.Control as="textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Write a comment" />
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formBasicCheckbox">
                    <Col sm="2"></Col>
                    <Col sm="10">
                        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Check me out" />
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                <hr />
                <Row>
                <Col sm="6">
                <Form.Group as={Row} >
                    <Form.Label column sm="4">Assignee</Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="8">
                    <Form.Control as="select" placeholder="Assignee">
                        <option>Unassigned</option>
                        <option>Ranjith</option>
                    </Form.Control>
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="exampleForm.ControlSelect1">
                    <Form.Label column sm="4">Milestone</Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="8">
                    <Form.Control as="select" placeholder="Milestone">
                        <option>No milestones</option>
                    </Form.Control>
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="exampleForm.ControlSelect1">
                    <Form.Label column sm="4">Labels</Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="8">
                    <Form.Control as="select" placeholder="Labels">
                        <option>No Labels</option>
                    </Form.Control>
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="exampleForm.ControlSelect1">
                    <Form.Label column sm="4">Weight</Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="8">
                    <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter a number" />
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                </Col>
                <Col sm="5">
                <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="exampleForm.ControlSelect1">
                    <Form.Label column sm="4">Assignee</Form.Label>
                    <Col sm="8">
                    <Form.Control type="date" placeholder="Enter a number" />
                    </Col>
                </Form.Group>
                </Col>
                </Row>
                <hr />
            <Button variant="success" onClick={this.state.onChange}>Submit issue</Button>
            </Form>
        </Container>
    )
}
}

export default Newissue
